00:41:28,600 --> 00:41:30,200
Mom, I have to hang up.

657
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:32,400
I need to return the phone.

658
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:34,300
That's all. Bye-bye.

659
00:41:48,500 --> 00:41:50,600
Come on, I'll send you back.

660
00:41:50,600 --> 00:41:52,000
Don't worry. It's really close by.

661
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,200
I can head back myself.

662
00:41:53,200 --> 00:41:55,200
Do you have any cash?

663
00:41:57,000 --> 00:41:58,400
Nope.

664
00:42:01,200 --> 00:42:02,800
Take this. For emergencies.

665
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:04,200
Thank you. I'll pay you back.

666
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:06,000
We can deal with that after your phone is fixed.

667
00:42:06,000 --> 00:42:07,600
Let's go.

668
